Package client

Interface Summary
IClientCommand An interface implemented by various command handlers.
 

Class Summary
BackupCommand Implement the "backup" command in the client.
ChangeDirCommand Implement the cd or chdir command to change the current directory in the client config.
ClientConfig The client configuration such as list of devices, currently logged in device, selected device and current directory.
ClientWithToken The wrapper class around restlet's client to add the authentication token to be sent to the server.
CopyCommand Class to handle the cp or copy command.
DeviceCommand Handle the device or dev command to change the currently logged in device.
DevicesCommand Handle the devices or devs command to print the list of available devices.
ListCommand Handle the list or ls command to list the files.
LoginCommand Handle the login command, which is implicitly invoked by the client when launched and not already logged in.
LogoutCommand Handle the logout command.
RestoreCommand Handle the restore command.
RootDirCommand Handler to change or display the current local root directory for the user on a particular device.
SelectDeviceCommand Handle the select command to change or display the currently selected device.
